    "scenes": [
        {
            "id": "s1",
            "bg_color": "#44aade",
            "text": {
                "header": "Overview",
                "body": "<p>The core deliverable of the pre-sale phase is the <b>media plan</b>.</p><p>It’s like the first beats of song. That’s because it's our first opportunity to create a solid impression. And it's our first chance to recommend strategies to meet their goals. They send out their RFP to multiple publishers, looking to invest in the best media plans. </p><p>That's why we want our media plan to showcase:</p><ul><li>our expertise with our ad product catalog</li><li>our media strategy skills</li><li>the badassery that is you and your pod</li></ul>",
                "class": "align-center-wide"
            },
            "enter": [
                {
                    "id": "mic",
                    "type": "from",
                    "duration": 0.5,
                    "startTime": 0.3,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0.0,
                        "ease": "Back.easeOut"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "leave": [
                {
                    "id": "mic",
                    "type": "to",
                    "duration": 0.5,
                    "startTime": 0.3,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0.0
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "s2",
            "bg_color": "#1959b3",
            "text": {
                "header": "Who Does What?",
                "body": "<p>Remember! Media plans don't guarantee that clients will run their campaign with us. Media plans are just proposals that we send back to the client. Clients choose us to run their campaigns when we sign an insertion order. </p><p>In this lesson, let's focus on who does what when building a media plan. We'll also highlight the core resources and systems needed in the pre-sale phase.</p>",
                "class": "align-right"
            },
            "enter": [
                {
                    "id": "piano",
                    "type": "from",
                    "duration": 0.5,
                    "startTime": 0.3,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0.0,
                        "ease": "Back.easeOut"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "leave": [
                {
                    "id": "piano",
                    "type": "to",
                    "duration": 0.5,
                    "startTime": 0.3,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0.0
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "s3",
            "bg_color": "#44aade",
            "text": {
                "header": "Media Planning Roles",
                "body": "<p>Each teammate in a pod has a role in helping to develop the media plan. Many of these tasks overlap across a pod. You'll see this happen quite often throughout the life of a deal. </p><p class='pt-callout'>Click on each hat to get a list of the media planning responsibilities owned by each role.</p>",
                "class": "align-left"
            },
            "interaction": {
                "name": "cr_mediaplans_s3",
                "id": "cr-mediaplans-s3",
                "type": "clickReveal",
                "items": [
                    {
                        "header": "Account Executive",
                        "body": "<ul><li>Engages Client Services with the RFP</li><li>Develops initial media plan recommendations</li><li>Reviews media plan with the client for RFP alignment</li><li>Sends the media plan to the client</li><li>Submits and manages PYM pricing approval cases</li><li>Submits and manages COGS approval requests</li></ul>"
                    },
                    {
                        "header": "Account Strategist",
                        "body": "<ul><li>Develops initial media plan recommendations</li><li>Reviews media plan with the client for RFP alignment</li><li>Sends the media plan to the client</li><li>Submits and manages PYM pricing approval cases</li><li>Submits and manages COGS approval requests</li></ul>"
                    },
                    {
                        "header": "Campaign Specialist",
                        "body": "<ul><li>Enters first version of media plan into Slingshot</li><li>Pulls inventory forecasts</li><li>Revises media plan based on client feedback</li><li>Formats media plans using client templates</li><li>Enters plan details into the client's third party order management system</li></ul>"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "enter": [
                {
                    "id": "cr-mediaplans-s3",
                    "type": "from",
                    "duration": 0.5,
                    "startTime": 0.3,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "cr-mediaplans-s3 .reveal-item",
                    "type": "staggerFrom",
                    "duration": 0.3,
                    "startTime": 0.8,
                    "staggerOffset": 0.15,
                    "props": {
                        "autoAlpha": 0
                    }
                }
            ],
            "leave": [
